{"tid":1558992,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急！！ [正視聽] ！！國歌問題","createTime":"2019-09-10T15:43:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T00:47:10.000Z","uid":164585,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ec0bc0e729b51712c6cce246e495857e776fc0ea","tid":1558992,"uid":164585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:43:29.000Z","msg":"估唔到呢首歌凝聚咁多手足<br />\n但係 佢<span style=\"color: red;\">絕對唔係</span>一首 海闊天空，無盡 個類既<span style=\"color: red;\">打飛機歌</span>！！！！<br />\n<br />\n希望咁多位手足盡快背左佢 之後每次唱 就好似國際咁 例如美國 <br />\n右手放心口 個身唔好搖左搖右 唔好再拎手機拍片 眼望前方 <br />\n咁樣做既文宣絕對係最好 最有傳染力<br />\n<br />\n記得 唔係打飛機歌黎架 我地未贏架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F6ZxWQi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF6ZxWQi.jpg&h=28b14822&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JX1TGgZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJX1TGgZ.png&h=2f4dbec7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6566a61d04e076bcfece6828a92d2804887c8934","tid":1558992,"uid":164585,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:45:14.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10<br />\n<br />\n上網好多片都係變哂感情歌咁 左搖右擺 成個感覺就係打飛機歌 <br />\n世界上冇一首國歌個身體會咁<br />\n<br />\n唱既心情應該係要記得 幾千人被捕 死去既手足 而唔係笑笑口咁唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24fba214dc81cbe53cf4498efb0bd5eec8f80f43","tid":1558992,"uid":164585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:45:59.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"0e18672be972d68873324a659fd5cbd713641133","tid":1558992,"uid":164585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:46:49.000Z","msg":"依家個感覺真係打飛機歌 唔該懷住我地手足被捕既心情去唱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8362032b05243676a28325dab551599823741e96","tid":1558992,"uid":1315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e18672be972d68873324a659fd5cbd713641133","tid":1558992,"uid":164585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:46:49.000Z","msg":"依家個感覺真係打飛機歌 唔該懷住我地手足被捕既心情去唱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:47:14.000Z","msg":"無錯 推"},{"pid":"67634373d3a47ea024dc0ca6b6cb12bbe20cdd88","tid":1558992,"uid":164585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:47:48.000Z","msg":"自推 4/10"},{"pid":"d68938c9bf5a24247d14c37c4c96e6341235a765","tid":1558992,"uid":266617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:48:27.000Z","msg":"要尊重國歌"},{"pid":"49389b60f3fbe3d3af2f87d50b3eb5b836fb6d94","tid":1558992,"uid":20099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:48:51.000Z","msg":"推！態度正確，國歌要有國歌樣式"},{"pid":"764d11f36f4c8237cd36ac7fd325fd57744f7248","tid":1558992,"uid":164585,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d68938c9bf5a24247d14c37c4c96e6341235a765","tid":1558992,"uid":266617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:48:27.000Z","msg":"要尊重國歌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:49:36.000Z","msg":"係呀 但係好多片段大家個樣唔係太嚴肅 仲見到有人邊唱邊笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對唔對得住被捕手足同烈士呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果要唱打飛機歌 我唱海闊天空唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d26766fdc16bc7535e7ec2466c34fa7b8e519d","tid":1558992,"uid":292864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:49:58.000Z","msg":"首歌我聽咁多次都只會越聽越凝重，諗唔到點解會開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0663ab674a0789cd2451eed542b5136736724776","tid":1558992,"uid":9647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:50:23.000Z","msg":"我已經係右手放心口唱"},{"pid